title: Last of my T206 Cubs collection FS
author: Rascal1010

posts.post_title: Last of my T206 Cubs collection FS
posts.post_content:
I started collecting these in 2013, and at my high water point had 104 different Sweat Caporal Front/Back combinations of the Cubs.  Over the last couple of years I have been trading or selling off a good portion of my collection to pursue other card interests.  Now I have decided that with prices where they are, I will probably not attempt another run at this subset, so I am offering the balance of what's left for sale.  Some of the cards offered are extremely tough front/back combinations, including a good number of factory 350/25 & 350-460/25 & 42 backs. A couple of the cards listed are in the top 3-5 condition wise known to exist for their respective front/back combinations.  There were quite a few of these that I have only found 1 or 2 examples of that have been on the market over the last 9 years.
     I lieu of posting pictures of all of these cards, I am only putting up the complete list.  If you would like scans of the cards, I will be more than happy to email front/back scans of any of the cards.  I will take care of shipping costs, all cards will ship Priority Mail.  Payment via PayPal F/F is preferred, but I am willing to possibly accept other forms of payment.  "I'll take it" will own card over any [B]ongoing negotiations for the same card, I will try to get back to everyone as quick as I can, but I do have a day job, so requests during the day may have a little delay in getting replied to.
    Here is the complete list, and hopefully these cards can find new homes with some Net54 members.  You can reach me by PM or email [url]Asmusstephen@gmail.com[/url]
